articles.description: Payton Pritchard had 19 points and 10 assists, and Troy Brown Jr. also had a double-double to lead Oregon past Washington State 84-57 on Sunday night.
articles.headline: Pritchard, Brown lead Oregon to 84-57 win over Washington St

articles.description: Shep Garner scored 16 points and Tony Carr had 15 points to lead Penn State to a 74-52 victory over Illinois on Sunday night.
articles.headline: Garner, Carr help Penn State beat Illinois 74-52

articles.description: After scoring a team-high 23 points, Grayson Allen credits the good ball movement to set him up in the Blue Devils' 80-69 win over the Yellow Jackets.
articles.headline: Allen credits ball movement for open looks

articles.description: Devin Davis scored 16 points, Armoni Brooks had a double-double and Houston throttled Tulane 73-42 on Sunday to stay in a tie for second place in the American Athletic Conference standings with Wichita State.

videos.description: Payton Pritchard finds Elijah Brown cutting backdoor and he slams it home.
videos.headline: Oregon's Brown throws down nice dunk

videos.description: Mikyle McIntosh tries to spin towards the basket but De'Quon Lake rejects his shot with authority.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Lake is a force around the rim

videos.description: Victor Bailey Jr. finds Mikyle McIntosh cutting to the basket and he throws down a mean tomahawk slam.
videos.headline: Oregon's McIntosh throws down a nasty slam

videos.description: Elijah Brown hits a step-back 3-pointer as time expires in the first half.
videos.headline: Ducks' Brown hits the buzzer-beater

videos.description: Payton Pritchard sees the clock winding down and scores the layup before time runs out. ON the next possession Mikyle McIntosh finds Pritchard for the corner 3-pointer as time winds down.
videos.headline: Ducks' Pritchard beats shot clock twice

videos.description: Troy Brown gets the steal and throws down the hammer in transition.
videos.headline: Ducks' Brown soars for nice jam

videos.description: Shannon Evans ll penetrates and finds the big man De'Quon Lake wide-open for the alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Evans-Lake connection leads to big dunk

videos.description: Troy Brown outlets a full-court pass to Elijah Brown who throws down the monster two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Ducks' Browns shows off in transition
